                <h6>Jennifer Farley Gordon</h6>
                <p>The short essay “Double Knits: Mid-Twentieth Century Mother-Daughter Sweaters” supplements the fascinating history of sweaters with a discussion of matching sweater trends for mid-twentieth-century mothers and daughters.</p>
